docs.lead_paragraph:
NEDERLANDER--James M.

The Association of Theatrical Press Agents and Managers mourns the passing of Broadway Theatre Owner and Producer James M. Nederlander, who employed countless members of this organization over the decades. He himself held the record for the longest running ATPAM membership on the books at 71 years, having joined in 1945. We extend our condolences to his family. The Board and Officers of ATPAM
